{"tid":1804584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[區議員入] 黃色經濟圈認證","createTime":"2019-12-31T05:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T11:05:37.000Z","uid":53766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81dc7dd50645a6d05b58eebbc07d0a548e96b40e","tid":1804584,"uid":53766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"依家冇一個統一既標準或者app分辨黃藍店<br />\n黃藍地圖好多都係傳言, 有d舖點睇都唔黃, 話有阿姐同情學生, 話政府唔岩。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地共識係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔介意扮黃定真黃, 肯表態就係黃店</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">區議員可唔可以幫手派下海報, 肯貼既就係黃店!</span></span><br />\n一來可以係地區宣傳建立人氣, 為立法會準備。二來海報比較軟性, 較多店舖可以參與。當然有店舖肯貼文宣既, 就應該更大大力懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知依家有米豬連認證, 但店舖太少。要黃色經濟圈發大黎做先可以全民參與。"},{"pid":"afeb76123a68e7b38c9871646dc9853f28438f58","tid":1804584,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署 </ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=95866926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=ce703967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">share去tg</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">最後一日</span></span><br />\n3. 暫